      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.Item.KLDWy78B7F6XoiPP]{School Specialist}</p>\n<p>When you cast a divination spell of 1st level or higher, you gain a brief insight into an upcoming challenge and how you might overcome it. You can expend this insight as a reaction when you attempt a single skill check to gain an insight bonus equal to 1 + the divination spell’s level to checks with that skill until the end of your next turn. Your special insight fades if not used within 1 minute.</p>"
